#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Current Approach (Chappie)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Chappie builds a vector database from documentation, exports it, and publishes it as a Docker image. Dev services download this image when needed."
