#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid ""
"**RAG Benefits**:\n"
"- Reduces context window usage\n"
"- Provides focused, relevant information\n"
"- Works with smaller models"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid ""
"**Direct Documentation**:\n"
"- Simpler implementation\n"
"- No vector database maintenance\n"
"- Better for comprehensive understanding"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "The team continues to evaluate the best approach as LLM capabilities evolve."
