#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Test-Driven Development with Agents"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Holly emphasized the value of TDD when working with agents:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "The TDD Workflow"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Write the test first**: Define expected behavior"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Verify it fails**: Ensure the test catches the issue"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Have agent implement**: Let the agent write code to pass the test"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Review the solution**: Ensure quality and correctness"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Focused tests**: Tests target specific functionality, not just coverage"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Better reproducers**: Excellent for bug reports and issue reproduction"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Guided development**: Tests provide clear success criteria"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Reduced boilerplate**: Agents handle test setup code"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Caveat"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Asking agents to \"write tests\" without guidance often produces low-value tests that are \"paid by the line.\" TDD keeps tests meaningful and purposeful."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title =
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Spec-Driven Development"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "Philip and Max advocated for spending more time on specifications:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "The Spec-First Approach"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Define the plan**: Outline architecture and approach"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Persist the plan**: Save it for reference"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Follow the plan**: Have the agent implement according to spec"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Iterate on the plan**: Refine based on results"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Better results**: More time planning = better implementation"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Clearer communication**: Specs serve as documentation"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Easier review**: Reviewers understand the intent"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-01-quarkus-insights-249-coding-agents.adoc
msgid "**Reusable patterns**: Specs can be adapted for similar features"
msgstr ""

